    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop the<strong> brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p>",
