      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>ground coriander</strong>,<strong> ground turmeric </strong>and<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
