    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pilaf is cooking, heat a separate large dry pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
