    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>harissa yoghurt</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
