      "instruction": "<p>Once the couscous is tender, top the <strong>Morrocan-style pilaf </strong>with the<strong> salmon flakes </strong>and cook, covered, for 1-2 min further or until the salmon is warmed through – this is your <strong>Morrocan-style salmon & giant couscous pilaf</strong></p>",
